    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>One thing, regardless of how you initialize the field, use of the <code>final</code> qualifier, if possible, will ensure the visibility of the field's value in a multi-threaded environment.</p>\n"
  }, {
