      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@JanHorčička: I do not see a significant difference between <code>MyClass myField = new MyClass();</code> and <code>List&lt;Integer&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;Integer&gt;();</code>. So just treat them the same."
